biolockj.node

Class OtuNodeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • biolockj.node.OtuNodeImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OtuNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Kraken2Node, KrakenNode, MetaphlanNode, QiimeNode, RdpNode, SlimmNode

    public abstract class OtuNodeImpl
extends Object
implements OtuNode
    The default implementation of OtuNode is also the superclass for all WGS and 16S OtuNode classes. OtuNodes hold taxonomy assignment info, represents one line of ClassifierModule output. The assignment is stored in a local otuMap, which holds one OTU name per level (level-gaps allowed).
